  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Colombian Reintegration Agency&#x2019;s Education and Training Model for Reintegration</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM will contribute to the implementation of the Education and Training for Reintegration Model (MEFR) of the Colombian Agency for the Reintegration of People and Groups Elevated in Arms in targeted educational institutions. The project has three components: the improvement of teachers&apos; capacities to implement the MEFR; the educational progress of students under the MEFR, with emphasis on occupational and productive training according to their abilities and competencies; and the expansion of the knowledge of local authorities and professionals on the tools of the MEFR.</narrative>
  </description>
